title: A Christmas Carol (2012) (digital)
description:
And now back to our regularly scheduled programming...

--------------------------------------------------------

A Christmas Carol

Markosia, 2012, 69 pages

Writer: Stephen Stern
Artist: Doug Sirois

Superb full-color adaptation of Dickens' timeless classic. Sacrificing none of Dickens'rich language and filled with cinematic artwork, A Christmas Carol is a wonderfully faithful adaptation of the quintessential Christmas story
